{
  "stem": "15694.8",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then a neighbor said-- anyway, before he said the three-- if you don't [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] sit down over here, or if you don't stop, I'll call the guards.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was like-- like a-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, to be in such tension, and then, of course, you have to go back to normal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And to him I said, what does it matter?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are dead anyway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And whatever he mumbled, I didn't understand anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the moment, it passed, and I sat down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this moment-- at this moment, I almost felt relief, because what would have happened outside?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If one of us would have been hurt, the train probably wouldn't have stopped because, to be shot by the guards would-- you know, it's-- it's also unlikely because we were two sides on-- and-- and this speed, I don't think the bullet would have hit us.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But if we were hurt, what should the other one do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, it also-- I also thought-- but that was of course at a much later date-- this moment of relief is the syndrome, what I call the live another minute syndrome.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How many people, for the reason of this syndrome, live another minute, have missed the opportunity of escaping, or going away, or running away in the last minute, most of which probably would have ended in death anyway, and people knew it.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it would have been the death I was always thinking about.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I should be killed, it should-- should be by-- with a bullet in the back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyway [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the moment of relief that I haven't jumped was short.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Soon over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Soon it came back, the full weight of the thought of this is going to be the end.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
